item.title: My First Post
item.description: Markdown Here Visit the website. Get it for Chrome. Get it for Firefox. Get it for Safari. Get it for Thunderbird and Postbox. Get it for Opera. Discuss it and ask questions in the Google Group. Markdown Here is a Google Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Opera, and Thunderbird extension that lets you write email† in Markdown‡ and render them before sending. It also supports syntax highlighting (just specify the language in a fenced code block).
